    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798162,
    "reference_id": 21559,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><span>忌邪</span>（或<em>熱心</em><span>〔</span><em>zealous</em><span>〕</span>）：神熱切地保護祂子民的福祉，也熱切渴望他們對祂忠誠（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:4-Exod20:5\">出20:4–5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:23-Deut4:24\">申4:23–24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4\">6:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:1-Jer3:5\">耶2:1–3:5</a>）。</p></li><li><p>神的報應和忿怒不可與人類「報復」的心態混為一談。祂的作為源自祂的聖潔（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:28-Jer50:29\">耶50:28–29</a>）、公義（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:1-Isa63:9\">賽63:1–9</a>），以及祂對子民的約的信實（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:23-Lev26:25\">利26:23–25</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:24-Isa1:26\">賽1:24–26</a>）。祂的報復從不是武斷的。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:2",
          "end_ref": "34001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798161,
    "reference_id": 21558,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:2–6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001002-34001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這首詩的第一節取材自紀念以色列出埃及的聖經經文。這個信息是，全地受造之物都在神主權的大能之下，祂必定懲罰一切敵對祂的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:2",
          "end_ref": "34001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798160,
    "reference_id": 21557,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:2–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001002-34001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這首短的兩節詩（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:2-Nah1:6\">1:2–6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7-Nah1:11\">7–11</a>）頌讚神掌管萬有的大能。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:2",
          "end_ref": "34001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798163,
    "reference_id": 21560,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><span>不輕易發怒</span>：神對悖逆的忍耐與祂信實的慈愛息息相關（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6\">出34:6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:18\">民14:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8\">詩103:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13\">珥2:13</a>）。這特質曾令約拿失望，因他希望尼尼微立刻被毀（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">拿4:2</a>）。因為神是<span>忍耐的</span>神，所以祂有時會延遲執行罪人當受的刑罰（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:29-Neh9:30\">尼9:29–30</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">羅2:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">彼後3:9</a>）；但那些持續犯罪的人最終必面對神的審判（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:7\">出34:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:10\">羅14:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">林後5:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:6-Rev14:7\">啟14:6–7</a>）。</p></li><li><p><span>旋風和暴風</span>：這意象描述了神對惡人施行審判時的忿怒（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:6\">賽29:6</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:3",
          "end_ref": "34001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798164,
    "reference_id": 21561,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>正如雲彩（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">1:3</a>）和山（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:5\">1:5</a>）一樣，海和江河也在神主權的掌管之下。舊約聖經中的先知常提及神在出埃及時對海和江河所行的作為（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:8-Exod15:10\">出15:8–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:16\">撒下22:16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:6\">詩66:6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:16\">77:16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:15\">哈3:15</a>）。神對水域的掌管，否定了古代迦南人的神話觀念——他們相信海與江河由海神淹（Yam）掌管。</p></li><li><p>巴珊位於加利利海的東方，以肥沃的牧場聞名，適合牧養牛群（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:14\">彌7:14</a>）。</p></li><li><p>迦密位於迦南中部的地中海沿岸，以其美景與豐產著稱（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:5\">歌7:5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:19\">耶50:19</a>）。</p></li><li><p>黎巴嫩以其巨大的香柏樹而聞名（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:6-1Kgs5:18\">王上5:6–18</a>）。那鴻列舉這些地方，是要表明即使是地上最肥沃、最富饒的地方，也不能抵擋神審判的權能。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:4",
          "end_ref": "34001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798165,
    "reference_id": 21562,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>舊約聖經中的詩歌常提到大地震動，以紀念出埃及時期的事件（例，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:7\">詩18:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:6\">哈3:6</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:18\">出19:18</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:5",
          "end_ref": "34001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798166,
    "reference_id": 21563,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>此處譯為忿怒的希伯來文詞重複了在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:2\">一章2節</a>出現的詞。此詞的重複使<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:2-Nah1:6\">一章2至6節</a>成為一個完整的詩歌段落。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:6",
          "end_ref": "34001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798168,
    "reference_id": 21565,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>耶和華本為善</span>：神在審判惡人時行事公正，並為信靠祂的人提供避難所。在人生的試煉中，祂接納並保護他們 （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">詩18:2</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:5-Ps62:7\">62:5–7</a>）。神豐富的美善能引領人悔改（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:2-Rom2:4\">羅2:2–4</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:7",
          "end_ref": "34001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:7"
        }
      ],
