    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798167,
    "reference_id": 21564,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:7–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001007-34001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這第二節詩（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"21557\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">1:2–11的研讀註釋</span>）集中描述神在對待全人類時所彰顯的主權、公義與公平。</p>",
