  {
    "content_id": 798169,
    "reference_id": 21566,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>漲溢的洪水</span>：這是一個形容神審判的力量極其強大的隱喻（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:6\">2:6</a>）。</p>",
