  {
    "content_id": 798170,
    "reference_id": 21567,
    "title": "那鴻書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你們為何策劃（和合本譯為：<span>尼尼微人哪，設何謀攻擊）</span>：任何針對神的圖謀或計劃都不可能成功。若不符合神的計劃，人所籌算的都是徒然的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:12\">詩2篇</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:26-Isa14:27\">賽14:26–27</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:9\">23:9</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 1:9",
          "end_ref": "34001009",
