  {
    "content_id": 798175,
    "reference_id": 21572,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>葡萄樹象徵神賜福祂的子民（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:2-Isa27:6\">賽27:2–6</a>），而被<span>毀壞</span>的葡萄樹則反映出神先前對他們的管教（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:1-Isa5:7\">賽5:1–7</a>）。與大衛和所羅門王時代相比，以色列人如今境況淒涼，但神應許要恢復祂子民的<span>榮華</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:2",
          "end_ref": "34002002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798176,
    "reference_id": 21573,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>車輛</span>因其靈活的機動性與強大的威力，在戰場上幾乎無可阻擋。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:4",
          "end_ref": "34002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:4"
        }
      ],
