    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798177,
    "reference_id": 21574,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>亞述王從尼尼微遭受襲擊的最初震驚中回過神來，向他的官員（和合本譯為：<span>貴冑）</span>大聲下令。他和全城都被打得措手不及，急忙衝向城牆阻擋圍攻。</p></li><li><p>設置他們的防禦（字面意思是<em>準備好遮蓋物</em>；和合本譯為：<span>預備擋牌</span>）：這裡的希伯來文的詞義並不明確，<em>遮蓋物</em>很可能是指攻城者或守城者用來防禦空中拋射武器的裝備。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:5",
          "end_ref": "34002005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798178,
    "reference_id": 21575,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>匆忙的防守行動（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:5\">2:5</a>）已為時過晚；城防已被攻破。</p></li><li><p>尼尼微依靠科斯爾河（Khosr River）上的雙重水壩所形成的水庫供水，科斯爾河是流經該城、屬於底格里斯（the Tigris ）河支流的一條河。這座水庫由一系列的閘門補充水量。希臘歷史學家狄奧多羅斯（Diodorus）記載，在那段時期的<span>滂沛</span>大雨已使該城的河流水系暴漲。尼尼微的攻擊者先關閉閘門，再將其打開，釋放積蓄的水，如同衝撞城牆的衝擊槌一般。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:6",
          "end_ref": "34002006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798179,
    "reference_id": 21576,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>由於尼尼微的被擄是神所命定的，因此這事必定會發生。</p></li><li><p><span>搥胸</span>是哀悼的常見表現（例，見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:13\">路18:13</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:7",
          "end_ref": "34002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798180,
    "reference_id": 21577,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>人民將會像水從被衝破的水庫中湧出般迅速逃離（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"21575\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">2:6的研讀註釋</span>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:8",
          "end_ref": "34002008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 21575,
          "content_id": 798178,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "那鴻書 2:6",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798181,
    "reference_id": 21578,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>亞述首都曾以貿易、進貢和戰利品積聚了來自列國的巨大且數不清的財富，但這些財富轉瞬即逝。殘暴的侵略和邪惡或許能暫時得逞，但最終必被毀滅（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:22\">箴13:22</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:15\">俄1:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:20\">路12:16–20</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:9",
          "end_ref": "34002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798171,
    "reference_id": 21568,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>掠奪、空蕩、毀滅（和合本譯為：<span>空虛荒涼）</span>：此處希伯來文以頭韻來增強語氣——buqah umbuqah umbullaqah。若譯成英文，其效果類似於「devastated, despoiled, and destroyed（<span>被破壞、被掠奪、被毀滅）</span>」。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:10",
          "end_ref": "34002010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798172,
    "reference_id": 21569,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:11–13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002011-34002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在描述尼尼微的滅亡（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:1-Nah2:10\">2:1–10</a>）之後，那鴻加入了三首諷刺詩中的第一首（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:8-Nah3:13\">3:8–13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:14-Nah3:19\">14–19</a>；這在古代近東是常見的文學形式）。在尖銳的諷刺中，他將尼尼微比喻為獅子的<span>洞</span>。西拿基立王和其他亞述王曾將自己比喻為獅子<em>，</em>甚至用獅子和自己獵獅的藝術圖像裝飾宮殿。然而，當神成為它的敵人時，尼尼微將不再是那無敵的掠食者的巢穴。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:11",
          "end_ref": "34002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798173,
    "reference_id": 21570,
    "title": "那鴻書 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>亞述驕傲的使者的聲音，可見於<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:19-2Kgs19:13\">列王紀下十八章19節至十九章13節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:13",
          "end_ref": "34002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798188,
    "reference_id": 21585,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>流人血的城</span>：亞述人殘忍暴虐的行徑有被詳細記載下來。他們的作法包括割下身體外部的器官——例如鼻子、耳朵、手和腳——以及將人釘死在木樁上。他們在被圍困的城門前堆積被砍下的頭顱。當受害者還活著時，他們也可能會挖出他們的眼睛，剝去他們身上的皮膚。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:1",
          "end_ref": "34003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798189,
    "reference_id": 21586,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:2–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003002-34003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這些簡短急促的片語，生動強烈地刻畫出戰爭畫面與聲音所帶來的震撼。</p></li><li><p>亞述的戰車與馭車戰士令人懼怕，使人聞之喪膽。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34003002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:2",
          "end_ref": "34003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798190,
    "reference_id": 21587,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>那美貌的妓女多有淫行</span>：亞述以財富和安全、繁榮的承諾誘惑列國，卻以軍事武力和經濟剝削加害他們。因此，他們所受的懲罰，是對其所行之事理所當然的公義報應（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:12\">箴24:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:4-Joel3:8\">珥3:4–8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:6\">啟18:6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">20:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:4",
          "end_ref": "34003004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798191,
    "reference_id": 21588,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神兩次對尼尼微說：<span>我與你為敵</span>（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:13\">2:13</a>）。尼尼微所受的審判就像是歷史的警戒，提醒世人耶和華憎惡罪惡，並必照著人的行為報應個人和列國（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7-Ps9:8\">詩9:7–8</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:12\">62:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:28\">耶46:28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">徒17:31</a>）。有一天，神公義的審判必臨到全地一切悖逆祂的人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:1-Rev19:21\">啟17–19章</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:5",
          "end_ref": "34003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798192,
    "reference_id": 21589,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>挪亞們是埃及歷史上的首都，位於上埃及尼羅河兩岸。在埃及強盛的新王國時期（公元前1550年-1069年），它作為政治、宗教和文化的中心而聲名最為顯赫。到了公元前600年代，雖然這座城不再是埃及的首都，但仍是一座繁榮的大都市。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:8",
          "end_ref": "34003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798193,
    "reference_id": 21590,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:9–10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003009-34003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>公元前663年，挪亞們被亞述王亞述巴尼拔（Ashurbanipal）攻陷。在亞述巴尼拔得勝之前，挪亞們似乎擁有不可征服的防禦能力，並得著全埃及以及其盟國的支持：古實、弗（可能是傳說中的邦特〔Punt<span>〕</span>之地，位於現今索馬利亞〔Somalia〕沿海附近），和利比亞。然而，這些盟友都未能有效保護挪亞們。</p></li><li><p><span>嬰孩......被摔死</span>：古代的征服者慣用這種極其殘忍的方式來滅絕敵人的嬰孩（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:12\">王下8:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:9\">詩137:9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:16\">賽13:16</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:18\">18</a>）。</p></li><li><p>士兵為爭奪戰利品而以<span>拈鬮來</span>決定分配，戰敗國的首領則被鎖上<span>鍊子</span>拘禁（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:7\">王下25:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:1\">耶40:1</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:4\">4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:3\">珥3:3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:11\">俄1:11</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "34003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:9",
          "end_ref": "34003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "NAM 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798182,
    "reference_id": 21579,
    "title": "那鴻書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "34003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>初熟的無花果</span>：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:1-Amos8:2\">阿摩司書八章1至2節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:13\">啟示錄六章13節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
